FBIS4-58112 "drnes084_n_94006" FBIS-NES-94-084 Daily Report 1 May 1994 LEBANON 'Arafat Opponent Injured in Combat Training 'Arafat Opponent Injured in Combat Training NC0105095494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 0930 GMT 1 May 94 NC0105095494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Arabic BFN [Text] A Palestinian source in the south has said that Munir Maqdah, former commander of the Fatah forces who is opposed to Yasir 'Arafat's policy, was hit by bullets and injured in the 'Ayn al-Hulwah camp yesterday while participating in combat training.
